<~>and<~>as<~>the<~>will<~>is<~>,<~>*NL*<~>so<~>does<~>its<~>action<~>and<~>its<~>world<~>become<~>.<~>Both<~>are<~>the<~>self-knowledge<~>of<~>*NL*<~>the<~>will<~>and<~>nothing<~>more<~>.<~>The<~>will<~>determines<~>itself<~>,<~>and<~>at<~>the<~>same<~>*NL*<~>time<~>both<~>its<~>action<~>and<~>its<~>world<~>;<~>for<~>besides<~>it<~>there<~>is<~>nothing<~>,<~>and<~>*NL*<~>these<~>are<~>the<~>will<~>itself<~>.<~>Only<~>thus<~>is<~>the<~>will<~>truly<~>autonomous<~>,<~>and<~>*NL*<~>from<~>every<~>other<~>point<~>of<~>view<~>it<~>is<~>heteronomous<~>.<~>Our<~>philosophical<~>*NL*<~>endeavours<~>can<~>only<~>extend<~>to<~>exhibiting<~>and<~>explaining<~>the<~>action<~>of<~>men<~>*NL*<~>in<~>its<~>inner<~>nature<~>and<~>content<~>,<~>the<~>various<~>and<~>even<~>opposite<~>maxims<~>,<~>*NL*<~>whose<~>living<~>expression<~>it<~>is<~>.<~>This<~>we<~>shall<~>do<~>in<~>connection<~>with<~>the<~>*NL*<~>preceding<~>portion<~>of<~>our<~>work<~>,<~>and<~>in<~>precisely<~>the<~>same<~>way<~>as<~>we<~>have<~>*NL*<~>hitherto<~>explained<~>the<~>other<~>phenomena<~>of<~>the<~>world<~>,<~>and<~>have<~>sought<~>to<~>*NL*<~>bring<~>their<~>inmost<~>nature<~>to<~>distinct<~>abstract<~>knowledge<~>.<~>Our<~>philosophy<~>*NL*<~>will<~>maintain<~>the<~>same<~>immanency<~>in<~>the<~>case<~>of<~>action<~>,<~>as<~>in<~>all<~>that<~>*NL*<~>we<~>have<~>hitherto<~>considered<~>.<~>Notwithstanding<~>Kant<~>'s<~>great<~>doctrine<~>,<~>it<~>*NL*<~>will<~>not<~>attempt<~>to<~>use<~>the<~>forms<~>of<~>the<~>phenomenon<~>,<~>the<~>universal<~>*NL*<~>expression<~>of<~>which<~>is<~>the<~>principle<~>of<~>sufficient<~>reason<~>,<~>as<~>a<~>*NL*<~>leaping-pole<~>to<~>jump<~>over<~>the<~>phenomenon<~>itself<~>,<~>which<~>alone<~>gives<~>meaning<~>*NL*<~>to<~>these<~>forms<~>,<~>and<~>land<~>in<~>the<~>boundless<~>sphere<~>of<~>empty<~>fictions<~>.<~>But<~>*NL*<~>this<~>actual<~>world<~>of<~>experience<~>,<~>in<~>which<~>we<~>are<~>,<~>and<~>which<~>is<~>in<~>us<~>,<~>*NL*<~>remains<~>both<~>the<~>material<