in<~>a<~>cloudy<~>form<~>on<~>the<~>farthest<~>horizon<~>of<~>consciousness<~>.<~>But<~>now<~>that<~>*NL*<~>there<~>is<~>room<~>,<~>this<~>prepared<~>material<~>at<~>once<~>comes<~>forward<~>and<~>occupies<~>*NL*<~>the<~>throne<~>of<~>the<~>reigning<~>care<~>of<~>the<~>day<~>-LRB-<~>πρυτανευουσα<~>-RRB-<~>.<~>And<~>if<~>it<~>is<~>*NL*<~>very<~>much<~>lighter<~>in<~>its<~>matter<~>than<~>the<~>material<~>of<~>the<~>care<~>which<~>has<~>*NL*<~>vanished<~>,<~>it<~>knows<~>how<~>to<~>blow<~>itself<~>out<~>so<~>as<~>apparently<~>to<~>equal<~>it<~>in<~>*NL*<~>size<~>,<~>and<~>thus<~>,<~>as<~>the<~>chief<~>care<~>of<~>the<~>day<~>,<~>completely<~>fills<~>the<~>throne<~>.<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>Excessive<~>joy<~>and<~>very<~>keen<~>suffering<~>always<~>occur<~>in<~>the<~>same<~>person<~>,<~>for<~>*NL*<~>they<~>condition<~>each<~>other<~>reciprocally<~>,<~>and<~>are<~>also<~>in<~>common<~>conditioned<~>*NL*<~>by<~>great<~>activity<~>of<~>the<~>mind<~>.<~>Both<~>are<~>produced<~>,<~>as<~>we<~>have<~>just<~>seen<~>,<~>*NL*<~>not<~>by<~>what<~>is<~>really<~>present<~>,<~>but<~>by<~>the<~>anticipation<~>of<~>the<~>future<~>.<~>But<~>*NL*<~>since<~>pain<~>is<~>essential<~>to<~>life<~>,<~>and<~>its<~>degree<~>is<~>also<~>determined<~>by<~>the<~>*NL*<~>nature<~>of<~>the<~>subject<~>,<~>sudden<~>changes<~>,<~>because<~>they<~>are<~>always<~>external<~>,<~>*NL*<~>can<~>not<~>really<~>alter<~>its<~>degree<~>.<~>Thus<~>an<~>error<~>and<~>delusion<~>always<~>lies<~>at<~>*NL*<~>the<~>foundation<~>of<~>immoderate<~>joy<~>or<~>grief<~>,<~>and<~>consequently<~>both<~>these<~>*NL*<~>excessive<~>strainings<~>of<~>the<~>mind<~>can<~>be<~>avoided<~>by<~>knowledge<~>.<~>Every<~>*NL*<~>immoderate<~>joy<~>-LRB-<~>exultatio<~>,<~>insolens<~>lætitia<~>-RRB-<~>always<~>rests<~>on<~>the<~>*NL*<~>delusion<~>that<~>one<~>has<~>found<~>in<~>life<~>what<~>can<~>never<~>be<~>found<~>there<~>--<~>lasting<~>*NL*<~>satisfaction<~>of<~>the<~>harassing<~>desires<~>and<~>cares<~>,<~>which<~>are<~>constantly<~>*NL*<~>br