*NL*<~>the<~>same<~>position<~>as<~>we<~>occupied<~>before<~>this<~>sorrow<~>or<~>desire<~>appeared<~>.<~>*NL*<~>All<~>that<~>is<~>even<~>directly<~>given<~>us<~>is<~>merely<~>the<~>want<~>,<~>i.e.<~>,<~>the<~>pain<~>.<~>*NL*<~>The<~>satisfaction<~>and<~>the<~>pleasure<~>we<~>can<~>only<~>know<~>indirectly<~>through<~>the<~>*NL*<~>remembrance<~>of<~>the<~>preceding<~>suffering<~>and<~>want<~>,<~>which<~>ceases<~>with<~>its<~>*NL*<~>appearance<~>.<~>Hence<~>it<~>arises<~>that<~>we<~>are<~>not<~>properly<~>conscious<~>of<~>the<~>*NL*<~>blessings<~>and<~>advantages<~>we<~>actually<~>possess<~>,<~>nor<~>do<~>we<~>prize<~>them<~>,<~>but<~>*NL*<~>think<~>of<~>them<~>merely<~>as<~>a<~>matter<~>of<~>course<~>,<~>for<~>they<~>gratify<~>us<~>only<~>*NL*<~>negatively<~>by<~>restraining<~>suffering<~>.<~>Only<~>when<~>we<~>have<~>lost<~>them<~>do<~>we<~>*NL*<~>become<~>sensible<~>of<~>their<~>value<~>;<~>for<~>the<~>want<~>,<~>the<~>privation<~>,<~>the<~>sorrow<~>,<~>*NL*<~>is<~>the<~>positive<~>,<~>communicating<~>itself<~>directly<~>to<~>us<~>.<~>Thus<~>also<~>we<~>are<~>*NL*<~>pleased<~>by<~>the<~>remembrance<~>of<~>past<~>need<~>,<~>sickness<~>,<~>want<~>,<~>and<~>such<~>like<~>,<~>*NL*<~>because<~>this<~>is<~>the<~>only<~>means<~>of<~>enjoying<~>the<~>present<~>blessings<~>.<~>And<~>,<~>*NL*<~>further<~>,<~>it<~>can<~>not<~>be<~>denied<~>that<~>in<~>this<~>respect<~>,<~>and<~>from<~>this<~>*NL*<~>standpoint<~>of<~>egoism<~>,<~>which<~>is<~>the<~>form<~>of<~>the<~>will<~>to<~>live<~>,<~>the<~>sight<~>or<~>*NL*<~>the<~>description<~>of<~>the<~>sufferings<~>of<~>others<~>affords<~>us<~>satisfaction<~>and<~>*NL*<~>pleasure<~>in<~>precisely<~>the<~>way<~>Lucretius<~>beautifully<~>and<~>frankly<~>expresses<~>*NL*<~>it<~>in<~>the<~>beginning<~>of<~>the<~>Second<~>Book<~>--<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>``<~>Suave<~>,<~>mari<~>magno<~>,<~>turbantibus<~>æquora<~>ventis<~>,<~>*NL*<~>E<~>terra<~>magnum<~>alterius<~>spectare<~>laborem<~>:<~>*NL*<~>Non<~>,<~>quia<~>vexari<~>quemquam<~>est<~>j