*NL*<~>Combinations<~>of<~>the<~>two<~>frequently<~>occur<~>.<~>Indeed<~>genuine<~>friendship<~>is<~>*NL*<~>always<~>a<~>mixture<~>of<~>selfishness<~>and<~>sympathy<~>;<~>the<~>former<~>lies<~>in<~>the<~>*NL*<~>pleasure<~>experienced<~>in<~>the<~>presence<~>of<~>the<~>friend<~>,<~>whose<~>individuality<~>*NL*<~>corresponds<~>to<~>our<~>own<~>,<~>and<~>this<~>almost<~>always<~>constitutes<~>the<~>greatest<~>*NL*<~>part<~>;<~>sympathy<~>shows<~>itself<~>in<~>the<~>sincere<~>participation<~>in<~>his<~>joy<~>and<~>*NL*<~>grief<~>,<~>and<~>the<~>disinterested<~>sacrifices<~>made<~>in<~>respect<~>of<~>the<~>latter<~>.<~>*NL*<~>Thus<~>Spinoza<~>says<~>:<~>Benevolentia<~>nihil<~>aliud<~>est<~>,<~>quam<~>cupiditas<~>ex<~>*NL*<~>commiseratione<~>orta<~>-LRB-<~>Eth<~>.<~>iii<~>.<~>pr<~>.<~>27<~>,<~>cor<~>.<~>3<~>,<~>schol<~>.<~>-RRB-<~>As<~>a<~>confirmation<~>*NL*<~>of<~>our<~>paradoxical<~>proposition<~>it<~>may<~>be<~>observed<~>that<~>the<~>tone<~>and<~>words<~>*NL*<~>of<~>the<~>language<~>and<~>caresses<~>of<~>pure<~>love<~>,<~>entirely<~>coincide<~>with<~>the<~>*NL*<~>tones<~>of<~>sympathy<~>;<~>and<~>we<~>may<~>also<~>remark<~>in<~>passing<~>that<~>in<~>Italian<~>*NL*<~>sympathy<~>and<~>true<~>love<~>are<~>denoted<~>by<~>the<~>same<~>word<~>pietà<~>.<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>This<~>is<~>also<~>the<~>place<~>to<~>explain<~>one<~>of<~>the<~>most<~>striking<~>peculiarities<~>*NL*<~>of<~>human<~>nature<~>,<~>weeping<~>,<~>which<~>,<~>like<~>laughter<~>,<~>belongs<~>to<~>those<~>*NL*<~>qualities<~>which<~>distinguish<~>man<~>from<~>the<~>brutes<~>.<~>Weeping<~>is<~>by<~>no<~>means<~>a<~>*NL*<~>direct<~>expression<~>of<~>pain<~>,<~>for<~>it<~>occurs<~>where<~>there<~>is<~>very<~>little<~>pain<~>.<~>*NL*<~>In<~>my<~>opinion<~>,<~>indeed<~>,<~>we<~>never<~>weep<~>directly<~>on<~>account<~>of<~>the<~>pain<~>we<~>*NL*<~>experience<~>,<~>but<~>always<~>merely<~>on<~>account<~>of<~>its<~>repetition<~>in<~>reflection<~>.<~>*NL*<~>We<~>pass<~>from<~>the<~>felt<~>pain<~>,<~>even<~>when<~>it<~>i